y></table>

**What this ranking means.** Rank #1 and #2 are the correct choices for the vast majority of buyers. They are the most affordable, the most proven at volume (363 and 478 reviews respectively), and the most faithful to The Silhouette Rule. Rank #4 and #5 are legitimate choices for buyers with specific aesthetic or practical priorities — bezel for stone security and a modern look, three-stone for a statement ring or a milestone purchase. Halo settings are not in this ranking because they do not serve The Silhouette Rule.

