## Lab Emerald Cut Engagement Ring: Where the Real Value Is

Lab-grown emerald cut diamonds at 2ct and above deliver the visual impact the shape requires — the long, wide face-up that makes the hall-of-mirrors effect read across the room — at a fraction of the natural price. A lab 2ct IGI D-FL Ideal emerald cut at $4,735 costs less than a natural 1ct D-VS1 stone at $3,140 — and the lab stone is visually twice as large.

